## Tickets (Linear)

Tickets live in Linear, workspace `<LINEAR_WORKSPACE>`, project `<LINEAR_PROJECT>`. Issue prefix: `<TICKET_PREFIX>-N`. The Linear Task Agent picks up tickets labelled `agent-eligible` and runs the `<RUNBOOK_COMMAND>` runbook.

**Never apply `agent-eligible`** to tickets that modify the agent's own launcher (`.claude/agent-profiles/code.yaml`) or runbook (`.claude/commands/<RUNBOOK_NAME>.md`) — self-modification is a recipe for non-recoverable state.

Authoring: `/new-ticket` (workspace-aware — detects this repo from cwd).

